@EduShield.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000

### Health Check
GET {{EduShield.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/health
Accept: application/json

### Test Public Endpoint
GET {{EduShield.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/test/public
Accept: application/json

### Dev Authentication
POST {{EduShield.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/dev
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "techtonicwave.business@gmail.com"
}

### Google Authentication (requires Google ID token)
POST {{EduShield.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/google
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idToken": "your-google-id-token-here"
}

### Test Authenticated Endpoint (requires Bearer token)
GET {{EduShield.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/test/authenticated
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Test Admin Only Endpoint
GET {{EduShield.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/test/admin-only
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Test Student Only Endpoint
GET {{EduShield.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/test/student-only
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Test Faculty Only Endpoint
GET {{EduShield.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/test/faculty-only
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Test Parent Only Endpoint
GET {{EduShield.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/test/parent-only
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Test Dev Auth Only Endpoint
GET {{EduShield.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/test/dev-auth-only
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Test Admin or Faculty Endpoint
GET {{EduShield.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/test/admin-or-faculty
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Get User Info
GET {{EduShield.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/test/user-info
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Refresh Token
POST {{EduShield.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "your-refresh-token-here"
}

### Revoke Token
POST {{EduShield.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/revoke
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "your-refresh-token-here"
}
